#: _versions/main/guides/spring-test.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Testing Spring-style Applications in Quarkus"
msgstr "еңЁ Quarkus дёӯжөӢиҜ• Spring йЈҺж јзҡ„еә”з”ЁзЁӢеәҸ"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/spring-test.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Spring developers migrating to Quarkus can keep using `@SpringBootTest` as they do in Spring Boot вҖ” no import change required.\n"
"Under the hood, Quarkus treats `@SpringBootTest` as an alias for xref:getting-started-testing.adoc[`@QuarkusTest`]: it starts the Quarkus runtime and CDI container, not a Spring Application Context."
msgstr "д»Һ Spring иҝҒз§»еҲ° Quarkus зҡ„ејҖеҸ‘иҖ…еҸҜд»ҘеғҸеңЁ Spring Boot дёӯдёҖж ·з»§з»ӯдҪҝз”Ё `@SpringBootTest` вҖ”вҖ”ж— йңҖжӣҙж”№еҜје…ҘиҜӯеҸҘгҖӮеңЁеә•еұӮе®һзҺ°дёӯпјҢQuarkus е°Ҷ `@SpringBootTest` и§Ҷдёә xref:getting-started-testing.adoc[@QuarkusTest] зҡ„еҲ«еҗҚпјҡе®ғдјҡеҗҜеҠЁ Quarkus иҝҗиЎҢж—¶е’Ң CDI е®№еҷЁпјҢиҖҢйқһ Spring еә”з”ЁдёҠдёӢж–ҮгҖӮ"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/spring-test.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`@SpringBootTest` in Quarkus is cosmetic. It is equivalent to `@QuarkusTest` and starts the Quarkus CDI container (ArC), not a Spring Application Context. Spring classes and annotations are used only for reading metadata."
msgstr "Quarkus дёӯзҡ„ `@SpringBootTest` д»…жҳҜиЎЁйқўдёҠзҡ„еҢәеҲ«гҖӮе®ғдёҺ `@QuarkusTest` ж•ҲжһңзӣёеҗҢпјҢдјҡеҗҜеҠЁ Quarkus CDI е®№еҷЁпјҲArCпјүпјҢиҖҢйқһ Spring еә”з”ЁдёҠдёӢж–ҮгҖӮSpring зұ»е’ҢжіЁи§Јд»…з”ЁдәҺиҜ»еҸ–е…ғж•°жҚ®гҖӮ"

